         You will be allowed to perform right shift operation any number of times. 

     One right shift operation will mean shifting all elements of the array by one 
     position in the right direction. The last element of the array will be moved to 
     the starting position in the array i.e. 0th index. 

     If it will be possible to obtain the sorted array by performing the above operation 
